OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAbolish Foreign Office,    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fformer top diplomats say   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Foreign Office should be abolished 
OL,6, and replaced by a new Department for   
OL,7, International Affairs with "fewer      
OL,8, colonial era pictures on the wall".    
OL,10,FThat is the conclusion of a group of   
OL,11,Fsenior former diplomats and officials  
OL,12,Fin a pamphlet proposing a radical      
OL,13,Freform of Britain's foreign policy.    
OL,15,FThey say the Foreign Office is elitist,
OL,16,F"rooted in the past" and "struggling to
OL,17,Fdeliver a clear mandate".              
OL,19,FIn response, the department said it had
OL,20,Fclearly defined priorities.            
